text: __NOTOC__ Year 84 BC was a year of the pre-Julian Roman calendar. == Events == === Roman Republic === * The First Mithridatic War comes to an end. == Births == * Catullus, Roman poet (approximate date) (d. c. 54 BC) * Surena, Parthian general (d. 52 BC) == Deaths == * Lucius Cornelius Cinna, consul, killed by mutinying troops Category:80s BC
title: 84 BC
